name: Bull Gravitas IIIα
description:
A gloaming sky, harakeke and tī kōuka murmured in the wind while a telephone pole stood silently waiting for a voice to break the spell.

Bull Creek, Aotearoa 🇳🇿

Hybrid print + digital
Process: photograph of this beautiful place –> hand drawing on copper plate –> ferric chloride etch –> aquatint –> ink –> press –> paper –> scanner –> vpype flow imager –> Illustrator –> 2500x2500px PNG.
